title.en: Ossan wa Uzeeeen da yo! tte Guild kara Tsuihou Shita Kuse ni, Go kara Fukki Yousei wo Dasarete mo Osoi. Saikou no Nakama to Deatta Ore wa Kocchi de Saikyou wo Mezasu!
